            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Shruti 1.1.1

This emergency audio-safety update fixes an echo/feedback loop discovered with Rogue
Amoeba audio routing and browser helper processes.

- Never captures `arkaudiod` or Nathaniel routing infrastructure as an app source.
- Removes blocked routing processes from older saved Shruti configurations.
- Fixes Safari/WebKit helper attribution in the watchdog so a live browser tap is not
  destroyed and rebuilt every two seconds.
- Keeps the direct path untouched after the incident reset.
]]></description>
